data.description: This unique and spacious Shawnee Heights A-frame home within walking distance to Shawnee Lake is up for grabs!  Check out the large fenced in backyard and the huge enclosed porch which includes a sauna and wiring ready for a hut tub!  Main level bathroom doubles as a concrete safe room.  This home is truly move-in ready with NEW roof, flooring and paint along with the updated bathroom and kitchen fully stocked with appliances!  Make an offer today and you may be able to call this your home for the holidays!
